reviewtext: As A Professional Audio Engineer, And An Amateur Photographer, I Take Many Pictures At Concerts...Kodak Is Good, But Never Comes Out Very Colourful, And The Generics Just Plain Suck...Fuji Film Really Brings Out All The Coloured Lights...The Oversaturation Of Colour Is Great, But Sometimes Unwanted...Agfa Is Good All Around Film, With Excellent Sharpness, But Tends To Be Expensive...Fuji Film Rules...
summary: Fuji Film - Oversaturated Colours Are Great, Sometimes...
